    "content": "**Welcome to SoftServe channel!** 👋\n\nHave questions about SoftServe? \nWho we are, what we do, or what it's like to work with us? This is the place.\n\nOur organizing team is here to answer questions about SoftServe as a company, career opportunities, our R&D practice, what working in our engineering teams looks like, and anything else you're curious about beyond the hackathon itself.\n\nFeel free to ask — we'd love to get to know you too!\n\n\nFor hackathon logistics and rules, check #rules-and-guidelines and #faq.\nFor technical questions about the assignment, head to #ask-mentors.",
