    "type": 0,
    "content": "You mentioned that all environment variables should be documented in an .env.example file.\n\nSince you might want to test our projects, we will likely need to include API keys as environment variables. Would you be able to provide us with some test API keys to include as examples in our submissions? This would help you test the projects more quickly.\n\nAlso, what if we use less common providers like OpenRouter? Of course you have API KEYS like ANTHROPIC_API_KEY or OPENAI_API_KEY, be preferred?",
